        "faq_item_kJtwLa": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is protein coffee?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky Instant Protein Coffee is a premium instant coffee blended with ultra-clean whey protein — giving you the energy of real coffee and the benefits of protein in one delicious scoop. It's designed for anyone who wants a smarter way to start their day, fuel their workouts, or simply enjoy a high-protein coffee without the hassle of brewing or blending.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_FnK3tU": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What ingredients do you use?",
            "answer": "<p>Our protein coffee is made with high-quality, carefully selected ingredients including Whey Protein Concentrate, real spray dried coffee, Psyllium Husk Powder (1,500 mg), Lion's Mane Mushroom Extract (300 mg), L-Theanine (200 mg), Caffeine Anhydrous (50 mg), and a Probiotic Blend (3 million CFU). It's sweetened naturally with Monk Fruit Extract and Fermented Reb M — no sugar, no artificial sweeteners. Each serving is just 67 calories with 10g of protein. All Franky Nutrition products are proudly made in the USA, 100% gluten-free, and non-GMO.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_p6JKzb": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where are your products manufactured?",
            "answer": "<p>We work exclusively with US-based manufacturers that follow strict quality control standards. All products undergo third-party lab testing to ensure purity, potency, and safety.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_kEt6g4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the shelf life of protein coffee?",
            "answer": "<p>Our Instant Protein Coffee has a shelf life of 2 years from the date of manufacture. Once opened, make sure to seal the bag tightly and store it in a cool, dry place to maintain freshness and quality.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
