    "faq_accordion_ieGUJc": {
      "type": "faq-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_EHJkkR": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How can protein coffee help me lose weight?",
            "answer": "<p>Protein is one of the most effective nutrients for supporting weight management. Franky Protein Iced Coffee may help you increase your daily protein intake, which may promote a feeling of fullness and may help reduce cravings and unnecessary snacking throughout the day. It may also support healthy digestion and may help fuel your body so you stay energized without reaching for sugary alternatives.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_gRdCBm": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What are the benefits of whey protein?",
            "answer": "<p>Whey protein is one of the highest-quality protein sources available. It is absorbed quickly and efficiently by the body and may support muscle growth while helping to reduce muscle breakdown. Whey protein may also support a healthy metabolism and fat burning, and contains essential amino acids critical for peak muscle performance. Additionally, it may support the body's natural antioxidant defenses and is highly satiating, helping to reduce hunger and cravings.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_XqGDgd": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Which fiber do you use and what are it's benefits?",
            "answer": "<p>Psyllium Husk is a natural plant-based fiber derived from the seeds of the Plantago ovata plant. Each serving of Franky Instant Protein Coffee contains 1,500 mg of Psyllium Husk Powder. It supports healthy digestion by promoting regular bowel movements and relieving occasional constipation. Psyllium Husk also acts as a prebiotic, feeding the good bacteria in your gut. Its high fiber content helps you feel fuller for longer, supports healthy blood sugar levels, and may contribute to maintaining healthy cholesterol levels.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_cyAWqY": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What are the benefits of the Probiotic Blend?",
            "answer": "<p>Each serving of Franky Protein Iced Coffee contains a probiotic blend of 3 million CFU featuring three clinically studied strains: L. acidophilus, B. longum, and L. plantarum.</p><p>These beneficial bacteria may support a healthy and balanced gut microbiome, which is essential for proper digestion and nutrient absorption. Probiotics may help reduce bloating and digestive discomfort, may support the gut lining, and may support a healthy immune response. A balanced gut has also been linked to improved mood, better energy levels, and overall well-being. Adding probiotics to your daily coffee is a simple way to may support your digestive health with every sip.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_DHQ4mn": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is Lion's Mane Mushroom Extract and what are its benefits?",
            "answer": "<p>Lion's Mane is a functional mushroom that has been used for centuries in traditional medicine. Each serving of Franky Protein Iced Coffee contains 300mg of Lion's Mane Mushroom Extract (Hericium erinaceus, fruiting body).</p><p>Lion's Mane is best known for may supporting brain health, mental clarity, and focus. Studies suggest it may promote nerve growth factor (NGF) production, which may support cognitive function and memory. It may also support the body's natural anti-inflammatory and antioxidant defenses, contributing to overall immune health.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_7J3AVq": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is L-Theanine and what are its benefits?",
            "answer": "<p>L-Theanine is a naturally occurring amino acid commonly found in tea leaves. Each serving of Franky Protein Iced Coffee contains 200mg of L-Theanine.</p><p>L-Theanine may promote a state of calm focus without drowsiness, making it the perfect complement to caffeine. When combined with caffeine, it may help smooth out the energy boost — supporting sustained focus and alertness without the jitters or crash. L-Theanine may also support relaxation, stress reduction, and improved sleep quality.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_RHBTji": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it safe to use during pregnancy or breastfeeding?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky Protein Iced Coffee contains caffeine, which should be monitored during pregnancy and breastfeeding. While the ingredients are generally considered safe, we always recommend consulting your healthcare provider before adding any new supplement to your routine during pregnancy or while nursing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_JhRzcn": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it safe to take alongside prescribed medication?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky Protein Iced Coffee is generally considered safe to use alongside medication. That said, we always recommend consulting your doctor or pharmacist before combining any supplement with prescribed medication, as individual circumstances vary.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_wF3grt": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is the protein coffee suitable for people with food allergies or dietary restrictions?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky Protein Iced Coffee contains milk derived from whey protein concentrate. If you have a dairy allergy or intolerance, this product may not be suitable for you. The product is 100% gluten-free and non-GMO. Please review the full ingredient list and supplement facts on the product label before purchasing if you have specific dietary concerns.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
