          "settings": {
            "question": "How can I contact customer support?",
            "answer": "<p>You can reach our team in three ways — by email at <a href=\"mailto:support@frankynu.com\">support@frankynu.com</a>, by phone at +1 (786) 442-1243, or via live chat in the bottom right corner of your screen. We're available Monday to Saturday, 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM ET and will get back to you as quickly as possible.</p>"
